<strong>Polished Mithril Torque - AC 7</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Slot: <a href="/armour/neck.shtml">Neck</a><BR>
Weight: 4.0 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/bard/armour/neck.shtml">BRD</a>, <a href="/monk/armour/neck.shtml">MNK</a>, <a href="/paladin/armour/neck.shtml">PAL</a>, <a href="/ranger/armour/neck.shtml">RNG</a>, <a href="/rogue/armour/neck.shtml">ROG</a>, <a href="/shadow_knight/armour/neck.shtml">SHD</a>, <a href="/warrior/armour/neck.shtml">WAR</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
(INT +13) (WIS +13) </font>
<BR>
Dropped in Solusek B by King Tranix.<BR>

