<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Well, I dont post much, but I feel this is warranted.<BR>
<BR>
I have been on Solb for about 3 weeks now doing KPC and Bugs/Bats and recently a group has moved in to the FG area.<BR>
<BR>
Well much to my surprise, last night I got a tell from one of those party members doing the FG raid asking if I wanted Skarlons's Sword!!!! It's NO DROP and 25/40 with Serpent Sight. Man i hightailed it to the corpse and looted that bad boy!<BR>
<BR>
Woohoo! Tonight the same bunch of guys were doing FGs and what dropped? One of these torques! So they gave me a tell and once again I made a quick swim in the lava to get to Tranix' corpse and loot it! I was amazed to say the least.<BR>
<BR>
My thanx go out to Trinket, Machera and their group for a fine display of what this game is all about: fun and comraderie (sp?). BTW all you stop griping about whos items are better and who is getting the shaft - like was said in an earlier post: the grass always SEEMS greener on the other side!<BR>
